column2: SELECT m.id as [id], str (m.ra, #, #) AS ra, str (m.dec, #, #) AS dec, n.distance, sp.ra AS ra2, sp.dec AS dec2, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (sp.type) as photo_type, str (sp.modelMag_u, #, #) as u, str (sp.modelMagErr_u, #, #) as err_u, str (sp.modelMag_g, #, #) as g, str (sp.modelMagErr_g, #, #) as err_g, str (sp.modelMag_r, #, #) as r, str (sp.modelMagErr_r, #, #) as err_r, str (sp.modelMag_i, #, #) as i, str (sp.modelMagErr_i, #, #) as err_i, str (sp.modelMag_z, #, #) as z, str (sp.modelMagErr_z, #, #) as err_z, str (pp.z, #, #) as photo_z, po.plate, po.mjd, po.fiberid, str (po.z, #, #) as spec_z into [myscratch:default].output_tdi_calibration from MyDB.input_tdi_calibration AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS sp ON n.objid = sp.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhoto AS po ON po.objID = sp.objID LEFT OUTER JOIN photoZ pp ON pp.objID = sp.objID ORDER by m.id
